data.description: Located on a level, cul-de-sac lot, this home is open concept with a kitchen island, separate dining room and office/living room, hardwood floors, granite counters, 9 foot ceilings, oversized owner's suite with 2 closets, separate shower and garden tub, double vanity, front porch, huge screened in back porch with fireplace and fenced in backyard. The subdivision has sidewalks throughout and beautiful lake with private resident access.
